lastfm.summary: “Milk it” is on Nirvana’s third studio album titled “In Utero”. The In Utero album was Released on September 13, 1993 and would become Nirvana’s final studio album. “Milk it” musical style could be described as very quiet verses accompanied by a very loud chorus. The lyrics written by Kurt Cobain contained depressing imagery that discussed Kurt Cobain’s frustration with fame & drug addiction. The lyrics also contain some of Kurt Cobain’s suicidal thoughts.
